org.hibernate.sql.model.internal

Packages that use org.hibernate.sql.model.internal
Package
Description
org.hibernate.dialect
This package abstracts over the multifarious dialects of SQL understood by the databases supported by Hibernate.
org.hibernate.dialect.sql.ast
Internal package containing dialect-specific extensions of AbstractSqlAstTranslator.
org.hibernate.sql.ast
Package defining a SQL AST for use in generation of SQL.
org.hibernate.sql.ast.spi
Package defining support for creating and consuming a SQL AST.
org.hibernate.sql.model.jdbc
Extensions to JdbcOperation for model mutations.
